{"ID":"20260609125043-pukub3d","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609125043-pukub3d","title":"2022年北京卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609125104-s461trk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125104-s461trk","updated":"20260609125104"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"又是一年槐花儿飘香的季节，小伙伴们有没有想起儿时那些带有妈妈专属味道的槐花美食？不过，槐花①"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。常见的槐花有三种：淡黄色的国槐花，夏末开花，可以入药②"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"；白色的刺槐花（也叫洋槐花），夏初开花，花香味甜，可食用但不可入药；红色的槐花（变种）仅供观赏，既不能食用，③"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。也就是说，我们吃的槐花美食来自白色刺槐。白色刺槐是我国重要的蜜源、食花和景观植物，原产北美。而我国土生土长的树种，是国槐。国槐在我国不只是一种常见的良木，而且作为一种文化元素融入传统文化之中。比如被奉为“神树”，种植在敬神祭祖的社坛周围；作为吉祥的象征，种在庭前屋后。古代社会，槐树还是三公（太师、太傅、太保）宰辅之位的象征，并出现了一些由“槐”字构成的具有政治寓意的词，如槐岳（朝廷高官）、槐蝉（高官显贵）、槐第（三公的宅第）等，槐树因此也受到读书人的喜爱。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125043-pzxd1uj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125043-pzxd1uj","updated":"20260609125116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609125116-l5vsdvc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125116-l5vsdvc","updated":"20260609125116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．请在文中横线处补写恰当的语句，使整段文字语意完整连贯，内容贴切，逻辑严密，每处不超过8个字。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125116-tqcn3zb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125116-tqcn3zb","updated":"20260609125116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"21．下列选项中，加点的词语和文中“槐蝉”所用修辞手法不同的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609125116-h2ps2bg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125116-h2ps2bg","updated":"20260609125116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．主人下马客在船，举酒欲饮无管弦。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125116-avsun1p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125116-avsun1p","updated":"20260609125116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．埋骨何须桑梓地，人生无处不青山。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125116-bg4rajx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125116-bg4rajx","updated":"20260609125116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．六军不发无奈何，宛转娥眉马前死。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125116-m6i8r0r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125116-m6i8r0r","updated":"20260609125116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．心非木石岂无感，吞声踯躅不敢言。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125043-35wxbmk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125043-35wxbmk","updated":"20260609125125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609125125-5piroey","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125125-5piroey","updated":"20260609125125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．①并不都是能吃的"}]},{"ID":"20260609125125-nzn3bm9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125125-nzn3bm9","updated":"20260609125125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②但不可食用"}]},{"ID":"20260609125125-ssko5l0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125125-ssko5l0","updated":"20260609125125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③也不能入药    21．D"}]},{"ID":"20260609125043-je8r999","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125043-je8r999","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-131r34l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-131r34l","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．本题考查学生语言表达之情境补写的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-emqnu9i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-emqnu9i","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一处，前面是说儿时对槐花美食的记忆，“不过”表转折，结合后面三类槐花的特点来看，有的可以食用，有的可以药用，而有的仅供观赏，所以此处填写“并非都能食用”这样的内容。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-oovlofb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-oovlofb","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二处，此处是说淡黄色国槐花的特点，“可以入药……”和后面洋槐花“可食用但不可入药”内容相对应，所以此处填写“但不可食用”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-i586raq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-i586raq","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第三处，此处是说红色槐花的特点，前面国槐花和洋槐花的特点是“可以入药但不可食用”“可食用但不可入药”，而此处的红色槐花“仅供观赏，既不能食用”，可见后面应是说“也不能入药”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-ds5bhkm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-ds5bhkm","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"21．本题考查学生正确使用常见的修辞手法的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-4lwbvk1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-4lwbvk1","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文中“槐蝉”是借代，代指高官显贵。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-6d4f08o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-6d4f08o","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．借代，用“管弦”代指音乐。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-kl1b1dz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-kl1b1dz","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．借代，用“桑梓”代指家乡。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-owma02p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-owma02p","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．借代，用“蛾眉”代指杨贵妃。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-l587s0z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-l587s0z","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．比喻，是否定喻，“人心”是本体，“木石”是喻体。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125144-v7t9qjn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125144-v7t9qjn","updated":"20260609125144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]}]}